  "response": "Jack Nicholson has largely stepped back from acting in recent years, which is primarily attributed to his advancing age and health concerns. While he is considered one of the greatest actors of his generation, he has not appeared in a film since \"How Do You Know,\" which was released in 2010. Reports suggest that he has been dealing with memory issues, which may have influenced his decision to step away from the spotlight. Nicholson has expressed a desire to focus on his personal life rather than pursue new roles, leading to his absence from recent cinema. However, fans of his work continue to hope for a return to the screen someday.",
